1
00:00:17,183 --> 00:00:18,184
Max.

2
00:00:20,770 --> 00:00:22,814
Max. Max, naririnig mo 'ko? Max.

3
00:00:23,440 --> 00:00:26,192
Sige na. Dumilat ka na. Ayan! Ganyan, Max!

4
00:00:27,027 --> 00:00:28,111
Naririnig mo 'ko?

5
00:00:28,778 --> 00:00:30,113
Max!

6
00:00:30,989 --> 00:00:32,615
Ayan! Dilat ka lang. Dilat ka lang.

7
00:00:33,283 --> 00:00:34,242
Itodo mo, Max.

8
00:00:34,325 --> 00:00:35,994
Ayan. Ganyan.

9
00:00:36,077 --> 00:00:37,454
Ayan! Ganyan nga!

10
00:00:43,168 --> 00:00:44,961
Hello, Lucas.

11
00:00:45,045 --> 00:00:49,591
Oo. Max. Kaya mo 'yan, Max. Ako 'to.
Nandito ako. Nandito ako, Max.

12
00:00:54,054 --> 00:00:58,767
Okay ka lang? May masakit ba?

13
00:01:00,101 --> 00:01:04,189
Wala akong masyadong maramdaman.

14
00:01:04,939 --> 00:01:07,859
Nararamdaman mo 'to? 'Yong kamay ko?

15
00:01:08,902 --> 00:01:09,819
Medyo.

16
00:01:10,320 --> 00:01:12,530
Nakakakita ka ba?

17
00:01:13,323 --> 00:01:18,578
Masyadong maliwanag 'yong mga ilaw.

18
00:01:19,621 --> 00:01:20,497
Uy.

19
00:01:21,081 --> 00:01:24,876
Matagal mong hindi nagamit
'yong mga mata at muscles mo.

20
00:01:25,919 --> 00:01:27,754
Mahina pa 'yong katawan mo,

21
00:01:27,837 --> 00:01:30,840
kailangan mo lang masanay at matuto ulit.

22
00:01:32,509 --> 00:01:34,094
Magiging okay ka rin.

23
00:01:35,261 --> 00:01:36,304
Magiging okay ka rin.

24
00:01:39,349 --> 00:01:41,101
Alam kong nandiyan ka pa rin.

25
00:01:42,477 --> 00:01:44,395
Alam kong di ka nawala.

26
00:01:46,356 --> 00:01:47,732
Nakita kita.

27
00:01:49,109 --> 00:01:50,652
Hinihintay mo 'ko,

28
00:01:50,735 --> 00:01:53,822
pinapatugtog mo 'yong kanta ko.

29
00:01:55,865 --> 00:01:57,075
Di ka ba nagsawa?

30
00:02:00,703 --> 00:02:01,913
Ikaw ba?

31
00:02:07,418 --> 00:02:08,503
Alam mo,

32
00:02:10,296 --> 00:02:11,756
na-realize ko,

33
00:02:13,883 --> 00:02:15,802
di ko naman pala kailangan 'yon.

34
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:19,722
Ikaw lang pala 'yong kailangan ko.

35
00:02:22,642 --> 00:02:23,935
Ikaw lang.

36
00:02:43,246 --> 00:02:44,122
Diyos ko.

37
00:02:44,205 --> 00:02:45,456
Max.

38
00:02:47,959 --> 00:02:51,004
Nandito ka na. Nandito ka na talaga.

39
00:02:51,087 --> 00:02:52,589
Nandito na ako.

40
00:02:53,381 --> 00:02:54,507
Welcome home, bata.

41
00:02:56,801 --> 00:02:58,052
Sarap ng tulog mo, a.

42
00:02:59,012 --> 00:03:00,388
Buwisit ka, Wheeler.

43
00:03:06,269 --> 00:03:07,353
Nasa'n ako?

44
00:03:08,771 --> 00:03:11,149
Oo, medyo nakakalito nga.

45
00:03:11,649 --> 00:03:13,776
Hinabol ka kasi ng mga Demo-dog,

46
00:03:13,860 --> 00:03:16,362
tapos no'ng malapit na nila tayong lapain,

47
00:03:16,446 --> 00:03:18,364
dumating si Mrs. Wheeler para…

48
00:03:19,616 --> 00:03:20,825
maglaba.

49
00:03:21,367 --> 00:03:23,411
Naks naman, Mama!

50
00:03:25,246 --> 00:03:26,206
Si Vecna.

51
00:03:28,249 --> 00:03:29,542
Magagalit siya.

52
00:03:30,460 --> 00:03:31,502
Hahanapin niya ako.

53
00:03:33,463 --> 00:03:35,465
Malalaman niyang nakatakas kami.

54
00:03:37,258 --> 00:03:38,635
Nasa'n si Holly?

55
00:03:40,845 --> 00:03:41,846
Nasa'n siya?

56
00:05:59,442 --> 00:06:00,777
Jonathan.

57
00:06:02,195 --> 00:06:03,404
Jonathan.

58
00:06:03,488 --> 00:06:04,530
Jonathan.

59
00:06:05,490 --> 00:06:06,783
Jonathan, tama na.

60
00:06:09,452 --> 00:06:10,536
Ano?

61
00:06:10,620 --> 00:06:13,414
Kung masasaktan tayo,
mas lalo lang lalala.

62
00:06:14,665 --> 00:06:16,209
Sa bagay.

63
00:06:19,128 --> 00:06:20,380
Hay naku.

64
00:06:23,174 --> 00:06:25,802
Okay, so ano na?

65
00:06:26,386 --> 00:06:27,887
May gusto ka pa bang aminin?

66
00:06:36,729 --> 00:06:37,939
Dito ka sa likod ko.

67
00:06:47,031 --> 00:06:48,408
Sorry kung natagalan kami.

68
00:06:53,246 --> 00:06:54,205
Ayos ka lang?

69
00:06:54,288 --> 00:06:57,208
Oo. Oo, ayos lang kami.

70
00:07:02,755 --> 00:07:03,756
Salamat.

71
00:07:05,675 --> 00:07:07,885
Ang weird ba? Sorry. Ang weird nga.

72
00:07:07,969 --> 00:07:10,430
Hindi ko… Akala… Akala namin…

73
00:07:10,513 --> 00:07:12,682
-Patay na kami? Akala rin namin, e.
-Oo.

74
00:07:12,765 --> 00:07:14,392
'Yong shield generator pala…

75
00:07:14,475 --> 00:07:16,769
Hindi pala shield generator.
Oo, alam namin.

76
00:07:16,853 --> 00:07:20,022
Mas maganda sana
kung sinabi n'yo sa 'min 'yan.

77
00:07:20,106 --> 00:07:21,732
Sinubukan namin.

78
00:07:21,816 --> 00:07:22,900
Naputol 'yong antenna.

79
00:07:22,984 --> 00:07:24,152
-Siya kasi.
-Siya kasi.

80
00:07:24,235 --> 00:07:26,904
E, ano 'yong binaril ko?

81
00:07:26,988 --> 00:07:28,448
Exotic matter.

82
00:07:28,531 --> 00:07:30,867
Alam ba dapat namin 'yon?

83
00:07:30,950 --> 00:07:33,536
Nandito lahat. Eto. Tingnan n'yo 'to.

84
00:07:34,871 --> 00:07:37,206
Notebook ni Dr. Brenner no'ng '83.

85
00:07:37,290 --> 00:07:39,041
Ginto ang notebook na 'to.

86
00:07:39,125 --> 00:07:43,379
Lahat ng research niya tungkol sa gate,
kung pa'no niya ginawa, kung ano 'yon.

87
00:07:43,463 --> 00:07:45,214
Inaalam ko pa 'yon, pero—

88
00:07:45,298 --> 00:07:47,175
Nakakatusta ng utak 'yan.

89
00:07:47,258 --> 00:07:50,386
CliffsNotes,
wala sa kabila ng pader si Holly.

90
00:07:53,222 --> 00:07:54,640
Nasa'n siya?

91
00:07:55,475 --> 00:07:57,602
Hindi ko alam.

92
00:07:57,685 --> 00:08:00,062
Pero kung nasa'n man siya,
hindi 'yon Upside Down.

93
00:08:21,542 --> 00:08:22,585
No'ng kinuha niya 'ko,

94
00:08:22,668 --> 00:08:25,046
nabuksan niya 'yong pang-apat
at huling gate,

95
00:08:25,129 --> 00:08:26,339
kaya nahati ang Hawkins.

96
00:09:05,253 --> 00:09:06,379
Kaya mo 'to.

97
00:09:33,823 --> 00:09:35,700
-Ano 'yon?
-Ang ano?

98
00:09:36,951 --> 00:09:37,868
Si Holly.

99
00:10:39,513 --> 00:10:46,520
CHAPTER SEVEN:
ANG TULAY

100
00:11:07,708 --> 00:11:08,668
Voyager Beta.

101
00:11:09,168 --> 00:11:10,086
May signal ka?

102
00:11:11,420 --> 00:11:14,090
Negative, Voyager Alpha. Voyager Gamma?

103
00:11:14,674 --> 00:11:16,425
Isang matabang zero dito.

104
00:11:17,093 --> 00:11:19,637
Palpak 'tong balloon experiment mo,
Snookums.

105
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:22,556
Ikabit na lang natin 'yong antenna sa van
tapos mag-drive tayo.

106
00:11:22,640 --> 00:11:25,184
Gaya ng sabi ko, Voyager Gamma,
dahil malubak 'yong daan

107
00:11:25,267 --> 00:11:26,727
at magubat sa Hawkins,

108
00:11:26,811 --> 00:11:30,564
hindi sasakyan ang pinakamabisang paraan
para ma-detect ang telemetry tag.

109
00:11:30,648 --> 00:11:34,276
"Mabisa"? Anim na oras kaya nating binuo
'yang lintik na balloon experiment mo!

110
00:11:34,360 --> 00:11:37,029
Oo nga, pero pag na-trilaterate natin
'yong tatlong signal,

111
00:11:37,113 --> 00:11:39,699
matutukoy ko na
'yong eksaktong location ni Dustin.

112
00:11:39,782 --> 00:11:42,493
Wala kang mata-trilaterate
kung wala tayong signal

113
00:11:42,576 --> 00:11:45,496
kaya putulin na natin ang kapalpakang 'to

114
00:11:45,579 --> 00:11:48,582
bago pa matigok 'yong star student mo.

115
00:11:49,750 --> 00:11:50,876
"Putulin…"

116
00:11:59,218 --> 00:12:01,095
Mas pinapalad ang matatapang.

117
00:12:04,432 --> 00:12:08,269
Nahanap ko na 'yong location ni Dustin.
Paliparin n'yo na ang mga lobo n'yo.

118
00:12:08,352 --> 00:12:10,020
-Pakiulit nga.
-Teka lang. Ano?

119
00:12:10,104 --> 00:12:14,066
Kailangan pa nating taasan.
Paliparin n'yo 'yong lobo n'yo.

120
00:12:18,195 --> 00:12:19,572
Negative 80!

121
00:12:20,197 --> 00:12:21,866
Negative 44.

122
00:12:21,949 --> 00:12:25,161
Binabawi ko na, Snookums,
henyo ka nga talaga!

123
00:12:25,244 --> 00:12:28,164
Salamat, Voyager.
Papasok na 'yong calculations. Sandali.

124
00:12:41,969 --> 00:12:45,264
Gagawin kitang espiya

125
00:12:46,432 --> 00:12:50,019
sa huling pagkakataon.

126
00:12:55,483 --> 00:12:56,317
Will.

127
00:12:58,194 --> 00:13:00,112
Nag-radio si Hopper.

128
00:13:00,196 --> 00:13:01,363
Ligtas na si Max.

129
00:13:01,447 --> 00:13:02,406
Nakalabas siya.

130
00:13:04,325 --> 00:13:07,077
Uy, magandang balita 'to.

131
00:13:07,995 --> 00:13:10,873
Hindi 'to mangyayari
kung hindi dahil sa 'yo.

132
00:13:10,956 --> 00:13:12,124
Magiging maayos din 'to.

133
00:13:12,792 --> 00:13:15,002
Pero hanggang kailan, Ma?

134
00:13:15,085 --> 00:13:17,880
Kung tama si Lucas, ngayon na 'yong araw,

135
00:13:17,963 --> 00:13:19,757
ngayon kikilos si Vecna.

136
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:22,718
Akala ko nahuli ko na siya.
Pero ang totoo…

137
00:13:23,969 --> 00:13:26,806
Ang totoo, wala akong kalaban-laban.

138
00:13:28,015 --> 00:13:31,727
At alam niya 'yon. Matagal na niyang alam.

139
00:13:31,811 --> 00:13:35,439
Kaya nga sa dinami-rami ng tao sa Hawkins,
ako ang pinili niya.

140
00:13:36,482 --> 00:13:43,072
Dahil alam niyang mahina ako,
at alam niyang mamamanipula niya 'ko.

141
00:13:43,155 --> 00:13:44,698
Hindi totoo 'yon.

142
00:13:44,782 --> 00:13:46,951
Totoo 'yon, Ma. Totoo 'yon.

143
00:13:47,034 --> 00:13:48,744
Naging kasangkapan niya 'ko,

144
00:13:49,745 --> 00:13:53,749
para gamitin 'yong kapangyarihan niya,
para maging espiya,

145
00:13:54,333 --> 00:13:56,585
at para bumuo.

146
00:13:57,878 --> 00:14:00,214
"Bumuo"?

147
00:14:00,297 --> 00:14:01,924
'Yong tunnels.

148
00:14:02,967 --> 00:14:05,010
Hindi 'yon kusang kumalat mula sa gate.

149
00:14:05,594 --> 00:14:10,933
Tuwing gabi, kumokonekta ako sa hive
at kinokontrol ko 'yong mga baging,

150
00:14:11,016 --> 00:14:12,852
ginamit ko 'yon para magka-tunnel,

151
00:14:12,935 --> 00:14:16,188
kaya kumalat sa mundo natin
ang Upside Down.

152
00:14:17,064 --> 00:14:19,358
Maraming namatay dahil sa 'kin.

153
00:14:20,484 --> 00:14:22,695
At kung nagawa ko lahat 'yon,

154
00:14:23,529 --> 00:14:27,032
ano pa'ng kaya niyang gawin
sa 12 pa na kagaya ko?

155
00:14:27,616 --> 00:14:29,159
Makinig ka.

156
00:14:29,243 --> 00:14:32,162
Wala kang kasalanan sa nangyari.

157
00:14:32,246 --> 00:14:33,080
Narinig mo?

158
00:14:33,664 --> 00:14:36,000
At 'yong malaking plano niya,

159
00:14:36,083 --> 00:14:39,086
wala na siyang 12 kasangkapan
o kung anumang tawag niya sa kanila,

160
00:14:39,169 --> 00:14:42,339
dahil nakatakas si Holly
at alam niya kung nasa'n 'yong iba.

161
00:14:42,423 --> 00:14:46,468
Anak, hindi pa tapos 'to,
mahaba pa ang laban.

162
00:14:47,636 --> 00:14:48,679
Mali ka.

163
00:14:49,471 --> 00:14:50,890
Mali ka, Mama.

164
00:14:51,432 --> 00:14:52,975
Kasalanan ko 'to.

165
00:14:53,058 --> 00:14:53,934
Hindi.

166
00:14:54,602 --> 00:14:55,853
Hindi, anak.

167
00:15:04,737 --> 00:15:06,280
Kilos na! Kilos na!

168
00:15:17,917 --> 00:15:20,169
Di ko nakita
kung sa'n magigising si Holly.

169
00:15:20,252 --> 00:15:22,880
Pero naisip ko,

170
00:15:23,923 --> 00:15:26,008
kung sa'n man siya tinago ni Vecna,

171
00:15:26,842 --> 00:15:28,802
nasa Upside Down lang 'yon.

172
00:15:30,220 --> 00:15:31,221
Kaya…

173
00:15:32,222 --> 00:15:35,601
ang sabi ko, umuwi muna siya.

174
00:15:35,684 --> 00:15:37,645
Umuwi? Saan? Sa bahay namin?

175
00:15:37,728 --> 00:15:40,064
So, kailangan nating bumalik
sa Upside Down.

176
00:15:40,147 --> 00:15:42,942
-Ano'ng pinakamalapit na bitak sa inyo?
-Sa Cornwallis yata.

177
00:15:43,025 --> 00:15:45,027
Siguro mga two and half kilometers.

178
00:15:45,110 --> 00:15:45,986
Lucas, copy mo?

179
00:15:46,070 --> 00:15:46,946
-Robin.
-Sige.

180
00:15:47,029 --> 00:15:47,863
Lucas!

181
00:15:50,282 --> 00:15:52,159
Erica, busy ako ngayon.

182
00:15:52,242 --> 00:15:56,080
Pinatay ni Vecna 'yong mga sundalo,
kaya madali nang makapasok sa MAC.

183
00:15:56,163 --> 00:15:57,915
May reinforcements na 'yon ngayon.

184
00:15:57,998 --> 00:15:59,750
Kaya kong alisin 'yong isang plate.

185
00:15:59,833 --> 00:16:04,213
Sinasabi n'yo ba na nakakulong si Holly
sa ilalim ng steel plate?

186
00:16:04,296 --> 00:16:06,548
Kung walang context,
nakakatakot pakinggan 'yon,

187
00:16:06,632 --> 00:16:10,260
pero hindi siya nakaipit sa ilalim
ng higanteng bakal. Ano lang…

188
00:16:10,344 --> 00:16:11,512
Pa'no ko ba sasabihin?

189
00:16:11,595 --> 00:16:15,057
-May mundo sa ilalim ng atin.
-Sa ilalim ng plates.

190
00:16:15,140 --> 00:16:16,225
Ang Upside Down.

191
00:16:16,308 --> 00:16:18,894
Oo, kagaya ng Hawkins,
mas pangit nga lang.

192
00:16:18,978 --> 00:16:22,356
Guys, guys, guys.
Okay, di kayo maniniwala dito.

193
00:16:22,439 --> 00:16:26,026
Nakakonekta sina Erica at Mr. Clarke.
Nahanap nila sina Dustin.

194
00:16:27,194 --> 00:16:30,781
Ayos. E di mas madali nilang mahahanap
si Holly kesa sa 'tin.

195
00:16:33,409 --> 00:16:35,953
Bilisan na natin. May bisita tayo.

196
00:16:47,923 --> 00:16:50,551
Uy. Okay lang kayo?

197
00:16:51,135 --> 00:16:52,428
Okay lang ako, Michael.

198
00:16:52,511 --> 00:16:54,888
Mawalang-galang na, Mrs. Wheeler,
pero hindi ka okay.

199
00:16:54,972 --> 00:16:58,100
Puwede kang magka-infection, hemorrhage,
at baka ikamatay n'yo pa.

200
00:16:58,600 --> 00:17:02,855
Kung iniisip mo na hihiga lang ako
habang nanganganib ang anak ko,

201
00:17:02,938 --> 00:17:04,648
nasisiraan ka na ng bait.

202
00:17:04,732 --> 00:17:06,025
Halika na.

203
00:17:06,108 --> 00:17:08,652
Mama. Mama, tama siya.

204
00:17:08,736 --> 00:17:10,279
Ako na'ng bahala. Una ka na.

205
00:17:10,863 --> 00:17:12,990
Ma, niligtas mo kami.

206
00:17:13,073 --> 00:17:14,533
Niligtas mo kami.

207
00:17:14,616 --> 00:17:17,244
At milagro na nandito pa rin kayo.

208
00:17:17,327 --> 00:17:20,414
Pero sa ngayon, magtiwala ka sa 'kin
na kami na ang tatapos nito.

209
00:17:20,497 --> 00:17:23,542
Baka marami pang gano'n do'n.

210
00:17:23,625 --> 00:17:25,335
Demogorgons 'yon. Alam ko.

211
00:17:25,419 --> 00:17:29,798
Marami akong kailangang sabihin sa inyo
tungkol sa Upside Down at kay El,

212
00:17:29,882 --> 00:17:31,633
pero ang kailangan mo lang malaman,

213
00:17:31,717 --> 00:17:34,887
'tong grupong 'to ang nagligtas kay Will
no'ng walang ibang may kaya.

214
00:17:34,970 --> 00:17:36,180
Kami 'yon.

215
00:17:36,263 --> 00:17:38,390
At gagawin din namin 'yon kay Holly.

216
00:17:38,474 --> 00:17:42,436
Ibabalik namin siya sa 'yo, Ma.
Promise ko 'yan. Okay?

217
00:17:44,021 --> 00:17:44,855
Okay?

218
00:17:56,200 --> 00:17:58,494
Mr. Clarke, salamat sa tulong, ha.

219
00:17:58,577 --> 00:17:59,661
Wag muna.

220
00:17:59,745 --> 00:18:02,289
Na-trilaterate namin
'yong position ni Dustin dito,

221
00:18:02,372 --> 00:18:03,749
sa mismong kinatatayuan ko.

222
00:18:03,832 --> 00:18:06,043
Pero pagdating namin, wala na siya.

223
00:18:06,126 --> 00:18:08,462
Wala siya diyan. Nasa ilalim siya.

224
00:18:09,463 --> 00:18:10,756
Ano?

225
00:18:11,507 --> 00:18:12,758
Di mo sinabi sa kanya?

226
00:18:13,300 --> 00:18:14,760
-Ano…
-Ang alin?

227
00:18:14,843 --> 00:18:16,512
Hala ka.

228
00:18:17,554 --> 00:18:18,847
Hala ka.

229
00:18:19,598 --> 00:18:21,308
Oy, halikayo dito! Dito!

230
00:18:23,143 --> 00:18:24,603
Nahanap ko siya!

231
00:18:24,686 --> 00:18:26,480
Nahanap ko si Dustin!

232
00:18:32,236 --> 00:18:33,946
-Wala akong marinig.
-Kumalma ka.

233
00:18:35,322 --> 00:18:37,825
May tao ba diyan?
Uulitin ko, si Dustin 'to.

234
00:18:37,908 --> 00:18:40,244
Dustin, si Mike 'to.
Nakatakas si Holly kay Vecna,

235
00:18:40,327 --> 00:18:42,371
at pupunta siya sa bahay namin
sa Upside Down.

236
00:18:42,454 --> 00:18:45,999
Pumunta ka agad do'n
at kitain mo si Holly. Copy mo?

237
00:18:46,083 --> 00:18:49,461
Wala sa bahay n'yo si Holly.
Nahanap namin siya. Uulitin ko—

238
00:18:49,545 --> 00:18:50,963
Dustin, nawawala ka.

239
00:18:51,672 --> 00:18:52,589
Dustin?

240
00:18:54,800 --> 00:18:58,387
Nasisiraan na ba 'ko,
o sinabi niyang nahanap niya si Holly?

241
00:19:00,347 --> 00:19:03,142
Okay, dumikit tayo sa pader na 'to.

242
00:19:03,225 --> 00:19:04,560
Bakit siya nasa lab?

243
00:19:04,643 --> 00:19:07,146
Nadaanan niya siguro
'yong lab papunta sa 'min.

244
00:19:07,229 --> 00:19:09,731
Tapos nakasalubong niya si Dustin?
Puwede ba 'yon?

245
00:19:09,815 --> 00:19:12,776
Malabo, pero oras na
para suwertehin naman tayo.

246
00:19:12,860 --> 00:19:13,694
Amen.

247
00:19:13,777 --> 00:19:17,322
Sorry. Di pa rin ako makasunod.
Nasa ilalim ng plates si Dustin?

248
00:19:17,406 --> 00:19:18,657
-Oo.
-Pero di siya nakaipit.

249
00:19:19,241 --> 00:19:20,576
Teka lang. Teka lang.

250
00:19:33,046 --> 00:19:35,465
Napapalibutan ng cameras 'yong bitak.

251
00:19:36,425 --> 00:19:38,760
Meron akong lumang spectrum analyzer
sa club.

252
00:19:38,844 --> 00:19:41,930
Kung mahahanap ko 'yong RF signal,
guguluhin ko 'yong transmission.

253
00:19:42,014 --> 00:19:42,931
Astig, a.

254
00:19:43,891 --> 00:19:45,642
Masyado mo namang ginalingan.

255
00:19:46,393 --> 00:19:49,104
Sinasabi mo ba na di madodoble
ni Alford 'yong score?

256
00:19:49,188 --> 00:19:50,856
Four from six mula sa field.

257
00:19:50,939 --> 00:19:54,026
Magiging bigatin si Reggie,
tandaan mo 'yan.

258
00:19:54,109 --> 00:19:55,360
Walang magagawa si Walsh…

259
00:19:59,364 --> 00:20:01,283
Patikim pa lang 'yan.

260
00:20:38,070 --> 00:20:39,947
Sama ka, Snookums?

261
00:20:40,030 --> 00:20:41,490
Papasok tayo?

262
00:20:42,658 --> 00:20:44,201
Papasok tayo.

263
00:20:46,203 --> 00:20:47,412
Steve!

264
00:20:47,913 --> 00:20:49,206
Dustin!

265
00:20:49,289 --> 00:20:50,123
Steve!

266
00:20:50,624 --> 00:20:52,125
Nancy! Holly!

267
00:20:52,209 --> 00:20:53,585
Jonathan!

268
00:20:59,883 --> 00:21:01,677
Hindi ba delikadong huminga dito?

269
00:21:01,760 --> 00:21:02,844
Di 'ko sure.

270
00:21:03,762 --> 00:21:04,721
Okay.

271
00:21:05,430 --> 00:21:07,808
Mike, kumusta kayo diyan?

272
00:21:07,891 --> 00:21:09,559
Mike? Mike!

273
00:21:11,228 --> 00:21:12,437
Nahanap na namin siya.

274
00:21:13,605 --> 00:21:15,274
Buti naman at nagkita tayo.

275
00:21:25,450 --> 00:21:26,410
Nancy?

276
00:21:28,120 --> 00:21:29,037
Nasa'n siya?

277
00:21:29,579 --> 00:21:30,872
Nasa'n si Holly?

278
00:21:36,503 --> 00:21:38,297
-Ano 'yon?
-Ang ano?

279
00:21:39,631 --> 00:21:40,507
Si Holly.

280
00:21:50,976 --> 00:21:53,770
Nancy! Nancy!

281
00:21:53,854 --> 00:21:55,564
-Holly! Holly!
-Nancy, tulong!

282
00:21:55,647 --> 00:21:58,191
-Nancy, tulong! Ibaba mo 'ko, please!
-Holly!

283
00:21:58,275 --> 00:21:59,943
Nancy! Nancy, please!

284
00:22:00,027 --> 00:22:00,902
Holly!

285
00:22:00,986 --> 00:22:02,654
Nancy!

286
00:22:08,869 --> 00:22:13,373
Para bang may nakahawak sa kanya,
pero di mo makita.

287
00:22:16,084 --> 00:22:17,252
Siya 'yon.

288
00:22:19,296 --> 00:22:21,173
Si Vecna 'yon. Wala nang iba.

289
00:22:22,883 --> 00:22:23,884
Mike?

290
00:22:23,967 --> 00:22:26,928
Ayos lang ba si Holly, Mike?
Mike, copy mo?

291
00:22:27,012 --> 00:22:29,473
Uulitin ko, ayos lang ba si Holly?

292
00:23:16,895 --> 00:23:18,897
Wag kang mag-alala, Holly.

293
00:23:19,856 --> 00:23:22,692
Malapit nang matapos 'to.

294
00:23:24,611 --> 00:23:28,532
Matatapos na 'to.

295
00:23:33,412 --> 00:23:36,540
Para siyang demonyo
na galing sa kabilang mundo.

296
00:23:37,207 --> 00:23:39,084
Kaya niyang kontrolin 'yong mga halimaw,

297
00:23:40,293 --> 00:23:41,586
pagalawin 'yong Humvees,

298
00:23:41,670 --> 00:23:43,130
patayin 'yong apoy.

299
00:23:45,757 --> 00:23:47,175
Di siya tinatalaban ng bala.

300
00:23:47,759 --> 00:23:49,261
Walang tumatalab sa kanya.

301
00:23:49,344 --> 00:23:50,887
Hindi na laban 'yon.

302
00:23:52,889 --> 00:23:54,641
Massacre na 'yon.

303
00:23:59,813 --> 00:24:03,275
Una, may mutant dogs sa ospital.
Ngayon naman may demonyo sa MAC.

304
00:24:03,358 --> 00:24:05,569
Ano pa'ng lalabas sa impiyernong 'yon?

305
00:24:05,652 --> 00:24:07,028
O magugulat na lang kami?

306
00:24:07,112 --> 00:24:09,948
Di ko alam kung napapansin mo,
pero nauubos na ang mga sundalo.

307
00:24:10,031 --> 00:24:11,700
May paparating nang reinforcements.

308
00:24:11,783 --> 00:24:14,870
Kung may request ka pa,
kausapin mo ang unit commander mo.

309
00:24:14,953 --> 00:24:17,581
Pa'no ko malalaman
kung di ko alam kung ano 'yong kalaban?

310
00:24:17,664 --> 00:24:21,626
Wala kang kalaban.
Hindi 'to gera. May hinahanap kayo.

311
00:24:21,710 --> 00:24:23,420
Pag may humarang, patayin mo.

312
00:24:23,503 --> 00:24:26,548
Pero kung wala,
tutukan n'yo 'yong paghahanap sa babae.

313
00:24:26,631 --> 00:24:29,134
Hanapin 'yong babae.
'Yan lang ba'ng alam mong sabihin?

314
00:24:29,217 --> 00:24:31,261
Paulit-ulit ka lang. Laruan ka ba?

315
00:24:33,763 --> 00:24:36,475
'Yong babaeng 'yon ang dahilan
kung ba't nangyari lahat 'to.

316
00:24:36,558 --> 00:24:39,186
Kung ginawa mo 'yong trabaho mo
at hinanap mo siya,

317
00:24:39,269 --> 00:24:40,645
di sana ako paulit-ulit

318
00:24:40,729 --> 00:24:42,731
at nasa atin sana
'yong mga halimaw sa Moscow

319
00:24:42,814 --> 00:24:45,942
at Soviets sana ang pinapatay nila
imbes na mga Amerikano.

320
00:24:46,026 --> 00:24:48,236
'Yong mga namatay, 'yong mga bata,

321
00:24:48,320 --> 00:24:50,906
nasa kamay mo ang dugo nila,
Lieutenant, wala sa 'kin.

322
00:24:51,490 --> 00:24:55,911
At kung ayaw mong sumunod sa kanila,
itikom mo 'yang bibig mo.

323
00:25:00,916 --> 00:25:03,585
Lt. Akers, Bravo One 'to. Copy?

324
00:25:06,129 --> 00:25:07,255
Oo, ano 'yon?

325
00:25:07,339 --> 00:25:09,424
May nakapasok sa bitak sa lumang lab.

326
00:25:10,217 --> 00:25:11,301
Papunta na 'ko.

327
00:25:19,226 --> 00:25:20,101
Okay ka lang?

328
00:25:20,936 --> 00:25:21,811
Max.

329
00:25:27,526 --> 00:25:32,989
Saglit lang akong nawala,
tapos naging sorcerer ka na?

330
00:25:33,073 --> 00:25:37,077
Hindi kaya saglit 'yon,
at saka di naman talaga ako sorcerer.

331
00:25:37,661 --> 00:25:39,120
Gano'n 'yong dating sa 'kin, e.

332
00:25:40,622 --> 00:25:42,916
Uy, gusto mong i-tour kita?

333
00:25:45,877 --> 00:25:48,380
Umeskapo na si Jimmy "Fast Hands"
bago pa mag-quarantine

334
00:25:48,463 --> 00:25:50,131
kaya lumipat kami dito.

335
00:25:50,215 --> 00:25:52,676
Nakatago sa likod ng bookshelf do'n
'yong basement.

336
00:25:52,759 --> 00:25:54,469
Hindi 'to Batcave, pero astig pa rin.

337
00:25:54,553 --> 00:25:57,305
Ginawa naming cover 'yong station.
Si Robin ang DJ.

338
00:25:57,389 --> 00:25:59,849
-Rockin' Robin.
-Rockin' Robin pala, sorry.

339
00:25:59,933 --> 00:26:01,393
Tapos si Steve ang sound man.

340
00:26:01,476 --> 00:26:02,394
Tingnan mo 'to.

341
00:26:15,699 --> 00:26:16,575
Uy.

342
00:26:17,534 --> 00:26:18,952
Mababawi natin si Holly.

343
00:26:19,035 --> 00:26:21,454
Mag-isa siya ro'n, Lucas.

344
00:26:22,038 --> 00:26:24,624
Mag-isa siya kasama ng halimaw na 'yon.

345
00:26:25,125 --> 00:26:27,961
Akala ko talaga makakalabas siya.

346
00:26:28,044 --> 00:26:29,504
Ang tanga-tanga ko.

347
00:26:30,088 --> 00:26:32,007
Kinailangan mong subukan.

348
00:26:32,591 --> 00:26:34,134
Hindi na dapat ako umalis.

349
00:26:36,636 --> 00:26:38,305
Pinrotektahan ko dapat siya.

350
00:26:39,347 --> 00:26:40,974
E di mayayari tayong lahat.

351
00:26:41,474 --> 00:26:44,352
Galing ka sa isip ni Vecna.
Matutulungan mo kaming talunin siya.

352
00:26:44,436 --> 00:26:46,855
Hindi. Wala akong maitutulong.

353
00:26:50,400 --> 00:26:52,819
Di ko nga alam
kung sa'n tinago ni Vecna si Holly, e.

354
00:26:52,902 --> 00:26:54,487
Mabuti na lang alam ko.

355
00:26:55,864 --> 00:26:58,408
Alam ko kung nasa'n siya,
di ko lang alam pa'no pumunta.

356
00:26:59,701 --> 00:27:01,453
May ipapakita ako sa inyo.

357
00:27:02,996 --> 00:27:03,913
Okay.

358
00:27:03,997 --> 00:27:09,044
Bale, ito ang Hawkins,
at ito ang Upside Down.

359
00:27:09,127 --> 00:27:12,464
Akala natin, ibang dimension
ang Upside Down na binuksan ni Brenner,

360
00:27:12,547 --> 00:27:15,592
pero ang totoo, tulay pala 'yon.

361
00:27:16,176 --> 00:27:19,929
Interdimensional bridge 'yon
na humahati sa space-time.

362
00:27:20,013 --> 00:27:23,683
Sobrang unstable no'n,
pero may exotic matter na kumakapit do'n

363
00:27:23,767 --> 00:27:27,062
na nakita namin
sa mismong gitna ng lab, sa ibabaw.

364
00:27:27,145 --> 00:27:28,438
Sa theoretical physics,

365
00:27:28,521 --> 00:27:30,857
-ang tawag sa ganitong tulay—
-Wormhole.

366
00:27:30,940 --> 00:27:33,943
At ang wormhole na 'to
ang nagkokonekta sa Hawkins dito,

367
00:27:34,027 --> 00:27:37,530
sa isa pang mundo na tatawagin kong Abyss.

368
00:27:37,614 --> 00:27:40,408
-May dahilan ba?
-Mundo ng kaguluhan at kasamaan.

369
00:27:40,492 --> 00:27:42,285
-Ano?
-D&D.

370
00:27:42,369 --> 00:27:43,870
-Anak ng teteng naman.
-Wow.

371
00:27:43,953 --> 00:27:47,832
Sa tingin ko sa Abyss na 'to nanggaling
'yong Demogorgons,

372
00:27:47,916 --> 00:27:48,833
'yong mga baging,

373
00:27:48,917 --> 00:27:51,961
'yong Mind Flayer, lahat ng nakakasulasok
na nasa Upside Down.

374
00:27:52,045 --> 00:27:54,047
Do'n mo tinapon si Henry noon.

375
00:27:54,130 --> 00:27:57,092
Matagal siyang nawala
at nakabalik lang siya dahil kay Brenner.

376
00:27:57,175 --> 00:27:59,010
Pinahanap niya si Henry sa 'kin.

377
00:27:59,094 --> 00:28:01,471
No'ng nagkaro'n ka
ng remote contact sa Abyss,

378
00:28:01,554 --> 00:28:02,555
do'n nabuo ang tulay.

379
00:28:02,639 --> 00:28:05,100
Mula no'n, ginamit 'yon ni Henry
at ng mga halimaw niya

380
00:28:05,183 --> 00:28:07,435
para tumawid pabalik sa Hawkins.

381
00:28:07,519 --> 00:28:09,771
Tinalo na natin si Vecna last year,

382
00:28:09,854 --> 00:28:13,066
pero mukhang bumalik lang siya sa Abyss
para magpalakas ulit.

383
00:28:13,149 --> 00:28:14,025
Duwag amputa.

384
00:28:14,109 --> 00:28:17,654
So, nagtatago lang pala si Vecna sa taas?

385
00:28:17,737 --> 00:28:19,906
Kaya pala wala tayong napala
sa mga crawl natin.

386
00:28:19,989 --> 00:28:22,951
-Kaya di ko siya mahanap sa bath.
-Kaya galing sa taas si Holly.

387
00:28:23,034 --> 00:28:24,953
Ba't niya dinala 'yong mga bata sa taas?

388
00:28:25,036 --> 00:28:26,538
Gaya no'ng ginawa niya sa 'kin.

389
00:28:26,621 --> 00:28:30,583
Mas mahina ang isip ng mga bata, tama?
Mas madaling bilugin at manipulahin.

390
00:28:30,667 --> 00:28:34,254
Ginamit niya akong daluyan ng isip
at powers niya para mas lumakas pa siya.

391
00:28:34,337 --> 00:28:35,880
Gagawin niya rin 'yon sa mga bata.

392
00:28:35,964 --> 00:28:37,632
"Para mas lumakas pa siya"?

393
00:28:38,174 --> 00:28:40,343
-Para saan?
-Para pagsamahin ang dalawang mundo.

394
00:28:42,512 --> 00:28:45,724
Ang sabi ni Holly,
sinabi raw ni Henry sa mga bata

395
00:28:45,807 --> 00:28:49,561
na tutulungan daw nila si Henry
para pagsamahin ang dalawang mundo.

396
00:28:50,687 --> 00:28:53,022
Di ko 'yon nagets no'ng una, pero—

397
00:28:53,106 --> 00:28:55,984
Gusto niyang ilipat 'yong Abyss,
ibabagsak niya sa Hawkins.

398
00:28:56,067 --> 00:28:56,943
Di niya ibabagsak.

399
00:28:57,527 --> 00:28:58,570
Pag-iisahin niya.

400
00:28:58,653 --> 00:29:02,323
Di nagpapalakas si Henry sa Abyss.
Gumagawa siya ng mga bitak.

401
00:29:02,407 --> 00:29:05,410
Para humina 'yong Abyss,
gaya ng ginawa niya sa Hawkins.

402
00:29:05,493 --> 00:29:07,203
Pag nag-abot ang Abyss at Hawkins—

403
00:29:07,287 --> 00:29:08,204
Magiging isa sila.

404
00:29:08,288 --> 00:29:09,664
Binabago niya 'yong mundo.

405
00:29:09,748 --> 00:29:12,834
Ga'no katagal kaya maglipat ng mundo?

406
00:29:12,917 --> 00:29:15,670
Isang ganito lang ba? O matagal?

407
00:29:15,754 --> 00:29:19,591
Sana matagal, dahil kung tama lahat 'to,
kailangan nating lumipad ng 2,000 feet,

408
00:29:19,674 --> 00:29:22,635
pasukin 'yong Abyss, iligtas sina Holly,
at patayin si Vecna

409
00:29:22,719 --> 00:29:24,345
bago magsanib 'yong dalawang mundo.

410
00:29:24,429 --> 00:29:28,099
Kung tama 'yong theory ko,
mamayang gabi na siya maglilipat ng mundo.

411
00:29:28,183 --> 00:29:30,018
Nasabi ko na ba na ayoko sa theory mo?

412
00:29:30,101 --> 00:29:31,144
-Ako rin.
-Pangatlo ako.

413
00:29:31,227 --> 00:29:33,813
Ayoko lahat 'to.

414
00:29:33,897 --> 00:29:37,317
Pero at least alam na natin
kung ano'ng haharapin natin

415
00:29:37,942 --> 00:29:39,194
at ang kailangang gawin.

416
00:29:40,570 --> 00:29:42,447
Kailangan lang natin ng plano.

417
00:30:03,718 --> 00:30:06,221
Sorry. Ayoko sanang makialam.

418
00:30:06,304 --> 00:30:09,307
Pero nag-aalala lang kasi kami.

419
00:30:10,391 --> 00:30:11,851
Okay lang ba siya?

420
00:30:18,024 --> 00:30:19,484
Pero nasabi mo na ba sa kanya

421
00:30:19,567 --> 00:30:22,362
na halimaw lang na nagpapanggap 'yong Max?

422
00:30:22,445 --> 00:30:25,073
Na pinaikot at niloko siya no'n?

423
00:30:25,156 --> 00:30:26,157
Oo naman.

424
00:30:26,908 --> 00:30:29,536
Ginawa ko na lahat,
pero ayaw niyang makinig.

425
00:30:31,120 --> 00:30:33,706
Kailangan natin siya mamaya,
kung hindi mabibigo tayo.

426
00:30:33,790 --> 00:30:36,376
Ano ba'ng sinabi ni Max sa kanya?

427
00:30:36,459 --> 00:30:39,462
Mga masasamang bagay.

428
00:30:40,088 --> 00:30:42,090
Sinabi niya na kinidnap ko raw kayo.

429
00:30:42,173 --> 00:30:43,842
-Ano?
-Niligtas mo nga kami, e.

430
00:30:43,925 --> 00:30:44,884
Kaya nga.

431
00:30:46,302 --> 00:30:48,012
May mas malala pa ro'n.

432
00:30:49,013 --> 00:30:52,976
Sabi niya, di ko raw ililigtas ang mundo.
Gusto ko raw wakasan 'to.

433
00:30:53,059 --> 00:30:56,312
-Ba't siya naniwala?
-Tanga siya, kaya siya naniwala.

434
00:30:56,396 --> 00:30:58,273
Hindi siya tanga, Thomas.

435
00:30:59,315 --> 00:31:02,944
Makapangyarihan ang halimaw na 'yon
at nagsisilbi siya sa Black Thing.

436
00:31:03,027 --> 00:31:04,737
Ginulo niya ang isip ni Holly

437
00:31:04,821 --> 00:31:07,699
at hinila niya si Holly mula sa liwanag
papunta sa dilim.

438
00:31:07,782 --> 00:31:11,160
Sumuko na lang kaya tayo at umuwi?

439
00:31:11,244 --> 00:31:13,246
-Umuwi?
-Kasama ng parents natin.

440
00:31:13,329 --> 00:31:14,455
Mamamatay tayong lahat.

441
00:31:14,539 --> 00:31:15,623
Ano ba'ng problema mo?

442
00:31:15,707 --> 00:31:16,958
Tumahimik ka, damulag.

443
00:31:17,041 --> 00:31:19,168
Puwede bang wag kayong mag-away-away?

444
00:31:19,252 --> 00:31:21,004
Alam kong naiinis kayo.

445
00:31:21,087 --> 00:31:22,672
Pero baka nga tama si Derek.

446
00:31:23,756 --> 00:31:27,468
Baka nga nabigo ako
at nanalo ang Black Thing.

447
00:31:28,344 --> 00:31:29,971
Hindi siya puwedeng manalo.

448
00:31:30,555 --> 00:31:32,223
Okay? Wag tayong pumayag.

449
00:31:33,516 --> 00:31:35,310
Mas kilala namin si Holly.

450
00:31:35,393 --> 00:31:39,147
Kinder pa lang, mag-best friend na kami.
Second-best friend niya si Debbie.

451
00:31:39,230 --> 00:31:41,441
-At crush niya si Josh.
-Hindi, a.

452
00:31:41,524 --> 00:31:42,692
-Totoo 'yon.
-Oo nga.

453
00:31:42,775 --> 00:31:46,571
Kung kakausapin namin siya,
baka umayos na siya.

454
00:31:47,488 --> 00:31:49,949
Baka maibalik namin siya sa liwanag.

455
00:31:50,617 --> 00:31:51,576
Tama si Mary.

456
00:31:51,659 --> 00:31:52,911
Magagawa namin 'yon.

457
00:31:52,994 --> 00:31:55,413
-Babalik siya sa liwanag.
-Babalik siya sa liwanag.

458
00:31:55,496 --> 00:32:01,210
Babalik siya sa liwanag.
Babalik siya sa liwanag.

459
00:32:01,294 --> 00:32:07,675
Babalik siya sa liwanag.
Babalik siya sa liwanag.

460
00:32:07,759 --> 00:32:12,096
Babalik siya sa liwanag.
Babalik siya sa liwanag.

461
00:32:14,807 --> 00:32:17,894
Sa security cameras, trench plate…

462
00:32:18,603 --> 00:32:19,854
Hindi bolt cutter 'yan.

463
00:32:20,355 --> 00:32:21,981
Posible nga, sir.

464
00:32:28,696 --> 00:32:30,114
Nagiging pabaya na siya.

465
00:32:31,199 --> 00:32:32,408
Padalos‑dalos.

466
00:32:33,076 --> 00:32:34,452
Baka halimaw ang gumawa nito.

467
00:32:34,535 --> 00:32:36,746
Halimaw na naninira
ng padlocks at cameras?

468
00:32:37,246 --> 00:32:38,456
Parang di naman.

469
00:32:41,668 --> 00:32:42,669
Siya 'to.

470
00:32:44,712 --> 00:32:47,256
Tipunin mo 'yong buong team.
Sabihin mo magkarga na sila.

471
00:32:47,340 --> 00:32:48,466
Papasok tayo.

472
00:32:52,720 --> 00:32:57,642
Sa base, sa Upside Down,
may chopper na naghihintay.

473
00:32:59,519 --> 00:33:01,521
Lilipad tayo sa Abyss,

474
00:33:01,604 --> 00:33:03,856
papatayin natin ang salot,
ililigtas ang mga bata,

475
00:33:04,649 --> 00:33:05,817
at bababa na tayo.

476
00:33:05,900 --> 00:33:08,236
-Sino'ng magpapalipad no'n?
-Helicopter 'yon.

477
00:33:08,319 --> 00:33:10,029
-May pilot sila. Mamimilit tayo.
-Oo.

478
00:33:10,113 --> 00:33:12,115
Kidnapping plot na naman. Gusto ko 'yan.

479
00:33:12,198 --> 00:33:14,534
Pa'no palulusutin ng pilot
'yong chopper sa bitak?

480
00:33:14,617 --> 00:33:17,620
-Ano'ng sinasabi mo? Deretso lang tayo.
-Ano?

481
00:33:17,704 --> 00:33:19,414
-Tanga.
-Deretso lang?

482
00:33:19,497 --> 00:33:23,084
Nasa 40 feet 'yong lapad ng rotors.
Masyadong malaki. Di kasya 'yon.

483
00:33:23,167 --> 00:33:25,503
Sanay na si Steve d'yan,
pero sige pa rin siya, 'no?

484
00:33:25,586 --> 00:33:28,006
-Ano ba'ng problema mo?
-Nakakatawa kaya.

485
00:33:28,089 --> 00:33:29,132
Tumahimik nga kayo.

486
00:33:29,215 --> 00:33:33,553
Sige, kung may magic bean kayo,
sabihin n'yo lang.

487
00:33:33,636 --> 00:33:36,889
Kung wala, susugal tayo.
Lilipad tayo o mamamatay tayo.

488
00:33:36,973 --> 00:33:38,850
-Lilipad o mamamatay.
-E di patay tayo.

489
00:33:38,933 --> 00:33:41,769
Walang mamamatay
kung susunod tayo sa plano.

490
00:33:41,853 --> 00:33:43,813
Isip muna tayo ng ibang options bago—

491
00:33:43,896 --> 00:33:45,857
Oo. Baka mamatay tayo.

492
00:33:45,940 --> 00:33:48,985
-Sabi mo 2,000 feet…
-Wag kang papayag, Jim.

493
00:33:49,068 --> 00:33:50,862
-Di kayo nakikinig sa isa't isa.
-Guys!

494
00:33:50,945 --> 00:33:52,071
Pa'no mo gagawin?

495
00:33:53,114 --> 00:33:54,073
"Magic bean…"

496
00:33:54,157 --> 00:33:55,950
Balik na tayo sa usapan, puwede?

497
00:33:56,034 --> 00:33:58,911
-Wag na tayong sumubok, gano'n?
-Jim, tingnan mo…

498
00:33:58,995 --> 00:34:00,079
Subukan nating…

499
00:34:00,163 --> 00:34:01,831
Di natin kailangan ng magic bean.

500
00:34:01,914 --> 00:34:03,249
-…eroplano!
-Di ko—

501
00:34:03,332 --> 00:34:04,709
Di na kailangan ng magic bean!

502
00:34:06,586 --> 00:34:10,048
Sorry. Di natin kailangan no'n.

503
00:34:10,882 --> 00:34:12,091
Ng magic bean.

504
00:34:12,175 --> 00:34:14,469
May beanstalk tayo dito.

505
00:34:22,351 --> 00:34:25,229
Okay, itong flashlight
'yong Squawk radio tower,

506
00:34:25,313 --> 00:34:26,481
ta's itong Slinky…

507
00:34:27,899 --> 00:34:29,067
'yong tulay.

508
00:34:29,609 --> 00:34:31,819
Di natin abot 'yong Abyss
mula sa tower, tama?

509
00:34:31,903 --> 00:34:35,031
Pero sabi ni Max, pag-iisahin ni Vecna
'yong dalawang mundo.

510
00:34:35,114 --> 00:34:37,200
Kaya hayaan natin siya.

511
00:34:37,825 --> 00:34:39,869
Tapos maghihintay tayo

512
00:34:39,952 --> 00:34:42,830
habang palapit nang palapit 'yong dalawa.

513
00:34:42,914 --> 00:34:46,375
Tapos pag malapit na
at pasok na sa bitak 'yong tower, bam!

514
00:34:46,459 --> 00:34:48,586
Kikilos na si El, magme-meditate siya,

515
00:34:48,669 --> 00:34:51,005
papasok siya sa isip ni Vecna
ta's tatambangan niya.

516
00:34:51,089 --> 00:34:52,215
Mukha mo, gago.

517
00:34:52,298 --> 00:34:55,051
Tapos ang spell
at hihinto sa paggalaw 'yong mga mundo.

518
00:34:56,010 --> 00:34:59,013
Wham, voilà!
May beanstalk tayo. Saktong-sakto.

519
00:34:59,597 --> 00:35:02,016
Kailangan lang nating akyatin 'yong Abyss.

520
00:35:02,100 --> 00:35:04,977
-Okay ako d'yan.
-Di naman imposible.

521
00:35:05,061 --> 00:35:07,063
-Salamat.
-Pero may isang malaking problema.

522
00:35:07,146 --> 00:35:09,232
Di ko maabot 'yong isip ni Vecna.

523
00:35:09,315 --> 00:35:10,817
Masyado siyang malayo.

524
00:35:10,900 --> 00:35:14,529
Di mo ba puwedeng subukan?
Lumantak ka ng maraming junk food.

525
00:35:14,612 --> 00:35:15,822
O kaya…

526
00:35:16,697 --> 00:35:17,824
ilalapit ka namin.

527
00:35:18,533 --> 00:35:21,119
Nasa baba ng lungga niya
'yong Upside Down lab.

528
00:35:21,202 --> 00:35:22,370
Di pa 'yon nagagalaw,

529
00:35:22,453 --> 00:35:25,331
kaya nando'n pa lahat
ng experiments ni Brenner, kasama na—

530
00:35:25,414 --> 00:35:26,666
'Yong bath.

531
00:35:26,749 --> 00:35:30,294
Kung makakapasok ka sa isip niya,
puwede kitang tulungan,

532
00:35:30,378 --> 00:35:31,337
gagabayan kita.

533
00:35:31,879 --> 00:35:33,589
Gamay ko na 'yong marumi niyang isip.

534
00:35:33,673 --> 00:35:35,091
Sasama rin ako.

535
00:35:35,174 --> 00:35:37,218
Nakadepende 'yong plano
sa pagpigil kay Henry.

536
00:35:37,301 --> 00:35:38,970
Sa ngayon, mag-isa si Jane sa laban.

537
00:35:40,179 --> 00:35:41,681
Di naman kailangang gano'n.

538
00:35:41,764 --> 00:35:44,100
Susundan ko si Jane sa isip ni Henry.

539
00:35:46,394 --> 00:35:48,938
Tatapusin natin ang kapatid natin
nang magkasama.

540
00:35:49,021 --> 00:35:51,732
Okay, sige, gusto ko 'yan.
Papatayin ng mag-ate 'yong kuya.

541
00:35:51,816 --> 00:35:53,651
Uwi natin 'yong mga bagets, heroes tayo.

542
00:35:54,235 --> 00:35:57,613
Kung tama si Lucas, wala na tayong oras,
kaya bilisan na natin.

543
00:35:57,697 --> 00:35:58,698
Last na.

544
00:35:58,781 --> 00:35:59,866
'Yong pang-finale.

545
00:35:59,949 --> 00:36:01,284
Habang palabas tayo,

546
00:36:01,951 --> 00:36:04,871
maghuhulog tayo ng bomba
malapit sa exotic matter.

547
00:36:05,913 --> 00:36:08,791
Magse-set tayo ng timer,
tatakas tayo sa Upside Down.

548
00:36:10,710 --> 00:36:13,796
Guguho 'yong tulay, kasama ng Abyss,

549
00:36:13,880 --> 00:36:18,092
ng Demos, ng Mind Flayer,
lahat 'yon mawawala.

550
00:36:18,801 --> 00:36:20,970
Tapos ang laro.

551
00:36:27,935 --> 00:36:29,312
Holly! Holly!

552
00:36:29,395 --> 00:36:32,690
Uy. Wag kang mag-alala. Ligtas ka na.

553
00:36:33,191 --> 00:36:35,526
Ligtas ka na. Kasama mo na kami. Okay?

554
00:36:38,696 --> 00:36:40,198
Welcome back, Holly.

555
00:36:40,281 --> 00:36:41,699
Welcome.

556
00:36:42,700 --> 00:36:43,618
Nasa'n siya?

557
00:36:44,202 --> 00:36:45,328
Si Mr. Whatsit?

558
00:36:46,454 --> 00:36:47,288
Nasa baba.

559
00:36:47,371 --> 00:36:48,497
Nag-aalala siya sa 'yo.

560
00:36:48,581 --> 00:36:49,624
Sobra.

561
00:36:49,707 --> 00:36:52,585
Hindi. Mary, makinig ka sa 'kin.

562
00:36:52,668 --> 00:36:55,796
Manloloko si Mr. Whatsit.
Di niya tayo niligtas.

563
00:36:55,880 --> 00:36:57,298
-Ki—
-Kinidnap niya tayo?

564
00:36:57,798 --> 00:37:01,093
Gusto niyang sirain 'yong mundo?
Holly, sinabi niya sa 'min lahat.

565
00:37:01,177 --> 00:37:04,055
Kasinungalingan 'yon.
Puro kasinungalingan!

566
00:37:04,138 --> 00:37:07,058
-Hindi! Hindi—
-'Yong babaeng nakilala mo, si Max.

567
00:37:07,558 --> 00:37:08,601
Di siya tao.

568
00:37:08,684 --> 00:37:09,644
Halimaw siya.

569
00:37:09,727 --> 00:37:10,853
Pinaikot ka niya.

570
00:37:10,937 --> 00:37:12,230
Hindi totoo 'yan.

571
00:37:13,356 --> 00:37:14,482
Kaibigan ko si Max,

572
00:37:14,565 --> 00:37:16,025
at tinutulungan niya tayo.

573
00:37:16,108 --> 00:37:19,695
Tinutulungan niya tayong makauwi
sa pamilya natin.

574
00:37:20,279 --> 00:37:21,405
Nakakulong tayong lahat.

575
00:37:21,489 --> 00:37:23,532
Sa isip ni Mr. Whatsit.

576
00:37:23,616 --> 00:37:26,285
Walang totoo sa nakikita n'yo!

577
00:37:26,786 --> 00:37:28,329
Maniwala kayo sa 'kin.

578
00:37:29,038 --> 00:37:29,914
Please.

579
00:37:30,498 --> 00:37:32,917
Maniwala kayo sa 'kin.

580
00:37:33,000 --> 00:37:34,835
Maniwala kayo sa 'kin.

581
00:37:34,919 --> 00:37:36,128
Kailangan n'yong maniwala.

582
00:37:38,839 --> 00:37:40,132
Derek.

583
00:37:41,968 --> 00:37:43,094
Sabihin mo sa kanila.

584
00:37:44,845 --> 00:37:46,722
Sabihin mo! Sabihin mo!

585
00:37:54,480 --> 00:37:55,982
Tama sila, Holly.

586
00:37:56,065 --> 00:37:57,608
Niloko lang tayo ni Max.

587
00:38:06,534 --> 00:38:07,451
Hindi ko…

588
00:38:07,952 --> 00:38:09,370
maintindihan.

589
00:38:10,246 --> 00:38:12,123
Lahat ng pinakita ni Max…

590
00:38:13,791 --> 00:38:16,002
parang totoo.

591
00:38:18,587 --> 00:38:20,673
Alam kong di ako dapat pumunta sa gubat.

592
00:38:20,756 --> 00:38:24,427
Pero pumunta pa rin ako, at…

593
00:38:25,636 --> 00:38:27,638
Pakiramdam ko…

594
00:38:30,975 --> 00:38:32,143
ang tanga-tanga ko.

595
00:38:32,768 --> 00:38:35,855
-Di ka tanga, Holly.
-Di mo kasalanan 'to.

596
00:38:35,938 --> 00:38:36,897
Holly.

597
00:38:37,898 --> 00:38:39,859
Ang importante, nandito ka na.

598
00:38:40,443 --> 00:38:41,944
Nandito ka na—

599
00:38:42,737 --> 00:38:44,238
Holly, tumigil ka!

600
00:38:49,118 --> 00:38:50,786
-Buwisit ka!
-Hawakan n'yo siya!

601
00:38:52,913 --> 00:38:54,165
Hawakan n'yo siya!

602
00:38:56,917 --> 00:38:57,752
Holly!

603
00:39:44,090 --> 00:39:49,261
Akala ko iingatan mo
'yong pagbagsak, pero…

604
00:39:50,179 --> 00:39:51,847
puwede na siguro 'yon.

605
00:39:54,266 --> 00:39:55,434
Walang anuman.

606
00:39:58,979 --> 00:40:01,690
Sa lahat naman
ng puwede niyang isama, siya pa.

607
00:40:02,733 --> 00:40:04,735
May tiwala si El sa kanya. Dapat tayo rin.

608
00:40:04,819 --> 00:40:08,239
Hindi, may binabalak siya.
Sigurado ako. Kaso…

609
00:40:09,240 --> 00:40:11,117
Di makikinig sa 'kin si El.

610
00:40:11,200 --> 00:40:13,577
Ano ba'ng nangyari sa inyong dalawa?

611
00:40:15,454 --> 00:40:17,206
Akala niya wala akong tiwala sa kanya.

612
00:40:18,249 --> 00:40:20,584
-Hindi totoo 'yon.
-Hindi talaga.

613
00:40:20,668 --> 00:40:22,336
Sinabi mo ba sa kanya?

614
00:40:23,087 --> 00:40:24,839
Akala niya di siya matatalo,

615
00:40:24,922 --> 00:40:26,590
pero hindi laging gano'n.

616
00:40:27,466 --> 00:40:29,468
Di naman 'yan 'yong tanong ko, e.

617
00:40:29,552 --> 00:40:32,805
Aayusin ko na lang 'yong sa 'min
pag natapos na 'to,

618
00:40:32,888 --> 00:40:36,308
pero sa ngayon, kailangan kong siguraduhin
na makakalabas siya nang buhay.

619
00:40:36,392 --> 00:40:40,312
Isang maling galaw lang ng Kali na 'yon,
mapapatay ko talaga siya.

620
00:40:40,813 --> 00:40:42,606
Papatayin ko siya. Di ako mag-aalangan.

621
00:40:42,690 --> 00:40:45,192
Kapag may nangyari kay El sa tank,
hihilahin ko siya.

622
00:40:46,652 --> 00:40:48,195
Di ko kayang mawala siya, Joyce.

623
00:40:51,490 --> 00:40:52,783
Di ko kaya.

624
00:40:58,330 --> 00:40:59,665
Huling crawl na 'to.

625
00:41:01,917 --> 00:41:03,127
Huling crawl na 'to.

626
00:41:17,391 --> 00:41:20,019
Sumasakit 'yong ulo ko
pag sinusubukan kong intindihin 'to.

627
00:41:21,479 --> 00:41:26,734
Pero C- yata 'yong grade ko sa physics,
kaya bahala na 'yong mga nerd.

628
00:41:28,110 --> 00:41:30,988
Tingin mo gagana 'yong plano?

629
00:41:31,071 --> 00:41:33,324
Dapat lang, 'no?

630
00:41:34,825 --> 00:41:36,827
Sana lang talaga nakakagalaw ako.

631
00:41:37,411 --> 00:41:38,746
Para kasing wala akong silbi.

632
00:41:38,829 --> 00:41:42,082
Kakailanganin ka nina El at Kali.
Ako nga 'yong walang silbi, e.

633
00:41:42,166 --> 00:41:44,293
Puwede ka pa ring pumunta sa Abyss.

634
00:41:44,376 --> 00:41:45,961
Masyadong delikado.

635
00:41:46,045 --> 00:41:49,590
Mapupunta ako sa pugad ng hive mind
at ewan ko kung ano'ng puwedeng mangyari.

636
00:41:49,673 --> 00:41:53,219
Huling lapit ko, ginawa niya 'kong spy,
at muntik ka nang mamatay.

637
00:41:53,302 --> 00:41:55,513
Niligtas mo rin ako, di ba?

638
00:41:55,596 --> 00:41:59,350
At saka ilang beses na 'kong muntik
na mamatay dahil sa gagong 'yon,

639
00:41:59,433 --> 00:42:01,477
kaya sanay na 'ko.

640
00:42:01,560 --> 00:42:05,940
Pa'no ka nabuhay sa isip ni Henry
nang gano'ng katagal?

641
00:42:06,023 --> 00:42:07,608
Suwertihan lang.

642
00:42:09,151 --> 00:42:10,611
May nakita akong kuweba.

643
00:42:11,195 --> 00:42:15,908
Lumang alaala niya 'yon
at takot na takot siya do'n.

644
00:42:17,284 --> 00:42:18,285
Ayaw niyang pumasok.

645
00:42:19,078 --> 00:42:20,913
Takot na takot siya.

646
00:42:20,996 --> 00:42:23,832
Sa ilalim ng mga peklat niya,
tao pa rin siya.

647
00:42:23,916 --> 00:42:28,462
Psychopath siya na may matinding ilusyon
ng pagiging diyos, pero…

648
00:42:29,964 --> 00:42:31,298
tao pa rin siya.

649
00:42:31,382 --> 00:42:34,760
Lahat naman siguro tayo
may kinakatakutan, 'no?

650
00:42:41,517 --> 00:42:44,186
OPERATION BEANSTALK
PAGHAHANDA SA MISYON

651
00:42:45,604 --> 00:42:47,815
Wheeler, kumusta 'yong contraption?

652
00:42:47,898 --> 00:42:52,903
Okay, kunwari itong bike bell
'yong remote trigger ng bomba.

653
00:42:52,987 --> 00:42:56,156
Pag dumikit 'yong wire
sa warrior na 'to, kaboom.

654
00:42:56,240 --> 00:42:57,157
Ang talino mo.

655
00:42:57,825 --> 00:43:00,828
Ewan ko lang kung kayang pasabugin
ang Upside Down

656
00:43:00,911 --> 00:43:02,830
ng malambing na tono ng Butthole Surfers.

657
00:43:02,913 --> 00:43:04,999
Binuo ko 'yong bomba,
ako ang pipili ng plaka.

658
00:43:05,082 --> 00:43:06,292
Puwede ka namang pumili.

659
00:43:06,375 --> 00:43:09,003
Pero 'yong maganda naman 'yong piliin mo.

660
00:43:09,086 --> 00:43:10,045
Maganda kaya 'to!

661
00:43:10,129 --> 00:43:12,840
Sa usapang save-the-world soundtracks,
sablay 'to.

662
00:43:12,923 --> 00:43:14,049
Ano'ng pipiliin mo?

663
00:43:14,133 --> 00:43:16,343
The Replacements. Wala nang iba.

664
00:43:16,427 --> 00:43:18,887
Tama na nga, Lester Bangs.

665
00:43:20,723 --> 00:43:22,308
Hoy. Hoy!

666
00:43:22,391 --> 00:43:24,184
Nakahawak ka na ba niyan dati?

667
00:43:24,268 --> 00:43:28,522
Hindi ganito, pero nakahawak na 'ko
ng BB guns, air rifles…

668
00:43:29,565 --> 00:43:30,399
Duck Hunt.

669
00:43:30,983 --> 00:43:32,026
Duck Hunt.

670
00:43:32,109 --> 00:43:33,402
Magaling kaya siya do'n.

671
00:43:35,821 --> 00:43:38,824
Pero may mas maganda 'kong naisip. Halika.

672
00:43:48,042 --> 00:43:50,502
Mas mabangis 'tong mga batang 'to,
wala lang sa itsura.

673
00:43:53,255 --> 00:43:54,590
Sigurado ka?

674
00:43:59,219 --> 00:44:00,179
-Uy, Dustin?
-O?

675
00:44:00,262 --> 00:44:03,515
Tungkol do'n sa mga nasabi ko kanina.
Gusto ko lang—

676
00:44:03,599 --> 00:44:05,976
-Wala 'yon. Okay lang 'yon.
-Hindi, kasi…

677
00:44:06,727 --> 00:44:07,853
Hindi okay 'yon.

678
00:44:11,023 --> 00:44:12,024
Si Eddie…

679
00:44:13,776 --> 00:44:15,152
Niligtas ka niya.

680
00:44:16,904 --> 00:44:18,072
Niligtas niya tayo.

681
00:44:19,156 --> 00:44:20,491
Alam ko kung ano siya sa 'yo.

682
00:44:20,574 --> 00:44:22,910
Di ko nga ma-imagine
kung ga'no kahirap 'yon, e.

683
00:44:23,452 --> 00:44:24,787
Pero imbes na…

684
00:44:26,664 --> 00:44:28,707
damayan kita, naging…

685
00:44:31,168 --> 00:44:34,046
Nagalit pa 'ko. Siguro…

686
00:44:36,674 --> 00:44:38,300
kaya ako nagalit dahil…

687
00:44:40,094 --> 00:44:41,470
hindi na tulad ng dati.

688
00:44:44,139 --> 00:44:45,057
Kasi…

689
00:44:46,975 --> 00:44:48,477
na-miss lang talaga kita.

690
00:44:52,773 --> 00:44:54,274
Na-miss ko 'yong best friend ko.

691
00:44:57,861 --> 00:44:59,738
Na-miss ko rin 'yong best friend ko.

692
00:45:13,210 --> 00:45:16,463
Para lang alam mo, di magandang sukatan
ng talino ang Rubik's Cube.

693
00:45:18,590 --> 00:45:21,635
'Yong beanstalk plan mo, seryoso,
genius lang ang makakaisip no'n.

694
00:45:21,719 --> 00:45:22,761
Siyempre…

695
00:45:23,804 --> 00:45:25,055
Kanino pa ba 'ko matututo?

696
00:45:25,139 --> 00:45:26,098
Tama ka naman.

697
00:45:26,640 --> 00:45:28,475
Ang kagandahan dito,

698
00:45:28,559 --> 00:45:30,519
kung papalpak 'to, pareho tayong dedbol.

699
00:45:31,437 --> 00:45:32,730
Patay ka, patay ako.

700
00:45:36,900 --> 00:45:37,901
Patay ka, patay ako.

701
00:45:56,044 --> 00:46:02,718
Bubuksan na 'yong gate
in five, four, three, two…

702
00:46:05,596 --> 00:46:06,847
Open sesame.

703
00:46:08,932 --> 00:46:09,850
Huli ka!

704
00:46:11,226 --> 00:46:13,312
Nakakuha na kami ng gate signal.
Uulitin ko.

705
00:46:13,395 --> 00:46:14,897
Nakakuha na ng gate signal.

706
00:46:14,980 --> 00:46:17,900
Pakisabi kay Snookums,
sakto ang timing niya! Mwah!

707
00:46:17,983 --> 00:46:20,027
Dahil ang sleigh ni Santa…

708
00:46:22,279 --> 00:46:23,947
ay halos handa na.

709
00:46:25,574 --> 00:46:27,284
Punyeta!

710
00:46:28,744 --> 00:46:31,079
Anak ng putakti naman, o!

711
00:46:31,622 --> 00:46:34,374
Bakit? Bakit? Bakit ngayon pa?

712
00:46:34,458 --> 00:46:36,001
Ano? Ayaw mo sa 'kin? Ha?

713
00:46:36,084 --> 00:46:38,212
Hindi ako! Hindi ako 'yon!
Hindi ako 'yong…

714
00:46:38,295 --> 00:46:39,129
Hi, sis.

715
00:46:39,213 --> 00:46:40,047
Hindi ako 'yong…

716
00:46:40,631 --> 00:46:41,715
Hi.

717
00:46:41,799 --> 00:46:43,675
Nagawa mo na ba 'to dati?

718
00:46:43,759 --> 00:46:45,719
May nakasama ka na ba sa isip mo?

719
00:46:48,096 --> 00:46:49,097
Ikaw ba?

720
00:46:49,932 --> 00:46:52,017
Lagi naming ginagawa 'to
ng psychic friends ko.

721
00:46:53,644 --> 00:46:55,395
Masaya akong nandito ako.

722
00:46:55,479 --> 00:46:56,355
Ako rin.

723
00:46:56,438 --> 00:46:58,023
Kahit pagkatapos no'ng kahapon?

724
00:47:00,317 --> 00:47:01,777
Napag-isipan mo na ba?

725
00:47:02,277 --> 00:47:03,695
'Yong ibig sabihin nito?

726
00:47:04,905 --> 00:47:07,699
Naisip ko na pag pinasabog natin
'yong tulay,

727
00:47:07,783 --> 00:47:10,327
sasabog din 'yong lab ni Dr. Kay.

728
00:47:11,286 --> 00:47:12,955
Matatapos na 'yong experiment niya.

729
00:47:13,038 --> 00:47:14,456
Gagawa ng bagong lab si Kay.

730
00:47:14,540 --> 00:47:15,624
Patayin natin siya.

731
00:47:15,707 --> 00:47:18,502
Siya 'yong pumalit kay Papa.
May papalit din sa kanya.

732
00:47:18,585 --> 00:47:20,712
E di tatakas tayo.
Magtatago tayo sa kanila.

733
00:47:20,796 --> 00:47:23,090
Sa lugar na may kahit isang waterfall?

734
00:47:24,758 --> 00:47:26,593
Pangarap lang 'yon, Jane.

735
00:47:26,677 --> 00:47:29,429
Kung tatakas kayo ni Mike,
magiging ligtas ka pansamantala.

736
00:47:29,513 --> 00:47:31,598
Pag nahanap ka nila, at mahahanap ka nila,

737
00:47:31,682 --> 00:47:35,310
papatayin nila si Mike,
gaya ng ginawa nila sa mga kaibigan ko.

738
00:47:35,394 --> 00:47:37,646
Tapos kukunin ka nila,
at gamit 'yong dugo mo,

739
00:47:37,729 --> 00:47:40,983
gagawa sila ng mas maraming bata
na magdurusa gaya natin.

740
00:47:41,066 --> 00:47:44,027
Gamit 'yong mga bata,
magbubukas sila ng marami pang gate,

741
00:47:44,111 --> 00:47:45,696
ng marami pang mundo.

742
00:47:45,779 --> 00:47:46,989
Di mo ba nakikita, Jane?

743
00:47:47,865 --> 00:47:49,157
Paulit-ulit lang 'to.

744
00:47:49,741 --> 00:47:52,786
Paulit-ulit na kalupitan at kasamaan.

745
00:47:53,871 --> 00:47:55,706
Pero puwede nating tapusin 'to.

746
00:47:57,040 --> 00:47:58,041
Mamayang gabi.

747
00:48:06,550 --> 00:48:07,801
Pa'no?

748
00:48:08,385 --> 00:48:10,262
Pag napatay na natin 'yong kapatid natin,

749
00:48:10,345 --> 00:48:12,180
pag naligtas na 'yong mga bata,

750
00:48:12,264 --> 00:48:14,224
di tayo sasama sa kanila.

751
00:48:14,725 --> 00:48:15,851
Di tayo aalis sa tulay.

752
00:48:15,934 --> 00:48:18,228
Pag nawala 'yong Upside Down…

753
00:48:21,523 --> 00:48:22,858
mawawala rin tayo.

754
00:48:24,902 --> 00:48:26,945
'Yon lang ang paraan, Jane.

755
00:48:27,613 --> 00:48:29,656
Ang tanging paraan.

756
00:48:33,785 --> 00:48:36,038
Tapos na kayong mag-meditate?

757
00:48:36,121 --> 00:48:39,207
Handa nang lumipad 'yong sleigh ni Santa!

758
00:49:05,901 --> 00:49:06,860
Mama?

759
00:49:12,074 --> 00:49:17,120
Kanina no'ng tinanong mo 'ko
kung ano'ng nangyari sa isip ni Vecna,

760
00:49:17,204 --> 00:49:19,456
di ko sinabi sa 'yo lahat.

761
00:49:22,668 --> 00:49:26,254
Kapag umatake si Vecna,
pahihinain ka niya,

762
00:49:26,338 --> 00:49:29,216
gagamitin niya ang isip mo laban sa 'yo,

763
00:49:29,758 --> 00:49:33,512
ilalabas niya lahat ng makakasakit sa 'yo.

764
00:49:34,304 --> 00:49:39,601
Kaya nilabanan ko siya
sa pag-focus sa masasayang alaala,

765
00:49:39,685 --> 00:49:42,270
'yong mga alaala ko no'ng bata ako,

766
00:49:42,771 --> 00:49:44,564
at no'ng di pa ako natatakot,

767
00:49:45,482 --> 00:49:47,234
at no'ng sobrang saya ko.

768
00:49:48,402 --> 00:49:50,946
Kaya ako nagkaro'n ng kontrol
do'n sa MAC-Z

769
00:49:51,029 --> 00:49:53,031
at kaya napatay ko 'yong Demos.

770
00:49:53,615 --> 00:49:55,701
Akala ko magagawa ko rin 'yon kay Vecna.

771
00:49:55,784 --> 00:49:57,452
Pero nakahanap siya ng paraan.

772
00:50:00,247 --> 00:50:01,957
May mga pinakita siya sa 'kin.

773
00:50:04,793 --> 00:50:07,546
Mga nakakatakot na bagay.

774
00:50:07,629 --> 00:50:09,006
Hindi, makinig ka.

775
00:50:09,089 --> 00:50:11,383
Kung anumang pinakita niya, di totoo 'yon.

776
00:50:11,466 --> 00:50:13,260
Pinapaikot ka niya. Sinungaling siya.

777
00:50:13,343 --> 00:50:15,429
Hindi siya nagsisinungaling.

778
00:50:16,596 --> 00:50:18,306
'Yong pinakita niya sa 'kin,

779
00:50:20,017 --> 00:50:21,768
hindi 'yon galing sa kanya.

780
00:50:23,186 --> 00:50:24,521
Galing sa 'kin.

781
00:50:26,314 --> 00:50:28,483
Nakikita niya lahat, Ma.

782
00:50:29,067 --> 00:50:31,778
Nakikita niya 'yong iniisip ko.

783
00:50:32,487 --> 00:50:34,322
Nakikita niya 'yong alaala ko.

784
00:50:34,990 --> 00:50:39,703
At nakikita niya 'yong mga sekreto ko.

785
00:50:40,579 --> 00:50:43,790
Pero sabi ni Max,
may kinakatakutan din si Vecna,

786
00:50:43,874 --> 00:50:45,792
at patunay 'yon na kaya ko siyang talunin.

787
00:50:46,501 --> 00:50:49,254
Pero para magawa ko 'yon,

788
00:50:50,756 --> 00:50:52,174
kailangan mong malaman…

789
00:50:56,720 --> 00:50:59,097
Kailangan mong malaman ang totoo.

790
00:51:03,769 --> 00:51:05,771
Sorry. May balita na kasi kay Hop.

791
00:51:05,854 --> 00:51:08,607
Fifteen minutes na siya sa biyahe.
Alis na tayo in five.

792
00:51:09,691 --> 00:51:11,068
Okay lang kayo?

793
00:51:11,151 --> 00:51:12,652
Sige, lalabas na rin kami.

794
00:51:14,613 --> 00:51:15,614
Teka lang.

795
00:51:16,907 --> 00:51:18,784
Tingin ko kailangan n'yong marinig 'to.

796
00:51:20,035 --> 00:51:21,161
Lahat kayo.

797
00:51:29,503 --> 00:51:30,420
Wala…

798
00:51:31,588 --> 00:51:35,801
Wala pa 'kong sinasabihan sa inyo nito

799
00:51:36,718 --> 00:51:37,719
kasi…

800
00:51:39,387 --> 00:51:44,684
kasi ayaw kong mag-iba
'yong tingin n'yo sa 'kin.

801
00:51:44,768 --> 00:51:46,478
Pero ang totoo…

802
00:51:47,521 --> 00:51:51,316
Ang totoo, iba naman talaga ako, e.

803
00:51:51,399 --> 00:51:52,609
Iba ako sa inyo.

804
00:51:53,819 --> 00:51:54,694
Nag…

805
00:51:55,445 --> 00:51:59,241
Nagkunwari lang ako na hindi
dahil ayokong maging iba.

806
00:51:59,825 --> 00:52:02,285
Gusto kong maging kagaya n'yo.

807
00:52:02,369 --> 00:52:04,287
Kagaya ng mga kaibigan ko.

808
00:52:05,372 --> 00:52:07,124
Kagaya n'yo rin naman ako.

809
00:52:07,207 --> 00:52:10,001
Kagaya n'yo ako sa halos lahat ng bagay.

810
00:52:10,085 --> 00:52:12,337
Mahilig tayong magpuyat kakalaro ng D&D.

811
00:52:12,420 --> 00:52:14,881
Gusto natin 'yong amoy-matanda
sa basement ni Mike.

812
00:52:14,965 --> 00:52:19,177
Nagba-bike tayo papuntang Melvald's
para sa Malted Milkshakes.

813
00:52:19,261 --> 00:52:22,013
At gusto nating maligaw sa gubat,

814
00:52:22,097 --> 00:52:25,058
maligaw sa Family Video
at magtalo kung ano'ng aarkilahin,

815
00:52:25,142 --> 00:52:27,853
tapos sa Holy Grail lang din naman
ang bagsak natin.

816
00:52:27,936 --> 00:52:31,523
Gusto nating may Milk Duds
'yong popcorn natin at extra butter.

817
00:52:31,606 --> 00:52:34,860
Mahilig tayong uminom ng Coke
na may Pop Rocks.

818
00:52:34,943 --> 00:52:37,821
Mahilig tayo sa bike races,
makipag-trade ng comics,

819
00:52:37,904 --> 00:52:41,700
sa NASA, kay Steve Martin,
at sa Lucky Charms at…

820
00:52:41,783 --> 00:52:43,285
Halos lahat na, e.

821
00:52:43,368 --> 00:52:47,164
Ayoko lang… Ayoko lang…

822
00:52:47,664 --> 00:52:48,582
Ayoko…

823
00:52:50,667 --> 00:52:51,585
Ayoko…

824
00:52:52,419 --> 00:52:53,461
Ayoko…

825
00:52:53,545 --> 00:52:55,380
Ayoko lang sa mga babae.

826
00:53:08,602 --> 00:53:09,561
Ibig kong sabihin…

827
00:53:10,478 --> 00:53:15,066
Gusto ko sila,
di nga lang tulad ng pagkagusto n'yo.

828
00:53:15,650 --> 00:53:19,738
Tapos meron akong crush

829
00:53:19,821 --> 00:53:22,908
kahit na alam ko na hindi siya katulad ko.

830
00:53:24,659 --> 00:53:27,537
Pero na-realize ko na siya 'yong Tammy ko.

831
00:53:27,621 --> 00:53:30,457
Ang ibig kong sabihin,
hindi talaga 'yon tungkol sa kanya.

832
00:53:30,540 --> 00:53:32,083
Tungkol 'yon sa 'kin.

833
00:53:32,167 --> 00:53:35,212
At akala ko tanggap ko na 'yong sarili ko,

834
00:53:35,295 --> 00:53:37,172
pero kanina,

835
00:53:37,672 --> 00:53:40,800
pinakita sa 'kin ni Vecna kung ano
ang mangyayari kung gagawin ko 'to,

836
00:53:40,884 --> 00:53:43,762
kung sasabihin ko sa inyo 'yong totoo.

837
00:53:44,346 --> 00:53:47,474
May pinakita siya sa 'king future,
at sa future na 'yon,

838
00:53:47,557 --> 00:53:51,061
nag-aalala sa 'kin 'yong iba sa inyo.

839
00:53:51,144 --> 00:53:53,271
Nag-aalala kayo na baka mahirapan ako.

840
00:53:53,355 --> 00:53:56,566
Tapos pakiramdam ko, may mali sa 'kin.

841
00:53:56,650 --> 00:53:58,193
Kaya tinaboy ko kayo.

842
00:53:58,276 --> 00:54:01,488
Tapos 'yong iba,
lumayo na lang nang lumayo

843
00:54:01,571 --> 00:54:05,283
nang lumayo nang lumayo
hanggang mag-isa na lang ako.

844
00:54:05,367 --> 00:54:08,954
Alam kong di nangyari 'yon
at di nakikita ni Vecna ang future.

845
00:54:09,037 --> 00:54:11,831
Pero nakikita niya 'yong iniisip natin
at may nalalaman siya.

846
00:54:11,915 --> 00:54:13,875
Para lang kasing totoo, e.

847
00:54:13,959 --> 00:54:16,503
Parang totoo talaga.

848
00:54:16,586 --> 00:54:19,631
Will. Makinig ka sa 'kin.

849
00:54:19,714 --> 00:54:22,092
Hindi mangyayari 'yon.

850
00:54:22,175 --> 00:54:24,052
Di ako mawawala sa 'yo.

851
00:54:24,970 --> 00:54:25,845
Kahit kailan.

852
00:54:25,929 --> 00:54:28,598
Okay. Okay.

853
00:54:29,224 --> 00:54:30,850
Di rin ako mawawala sa 'yo.

854
00:54:37,315 --> 00:54:38,233
Ako rin.

855
00:54:39,359 --> 00:54:40,235
Ako rin.

856
00:54:41,236 --> 00:54:42,195
Ako rin.

857
00:54:42,279 --> 00:54:43,154
Ako rin.

858
00:54:43,822 --> 00:54:44,864
Ako rin.

859
00:55:01,339 --> 00:55:03,550
Di mo na pala kailangan ng truth serum, e.

860
00:55:05,135 --> 00:55:08,305
Sorry. Nakakainis,
pero kailangan mo 'kong yakapin.

861
00:55:08,388 --> 00:55:10,640
Naku, Max.

862
00:55:14,352 --> 00:55:17,522
Isipin mo na lang
na niyayakap din kita nang mahigpit, ha?

863
00:55:17,605 --> 00:55:18,690
Okay.

864
00:55:27,407 --> 00:55:28,575
El.

865
00:55:29,200 --> 00:55:31,536
Alam kong kaya mong talunin si Vecna.

866
00:55:31,619 --> 00:55:34,205
Pero kaya niyang tumakas pabalik
sa pisikal na mundo

867
00:55:34,289 --> 00:55:37,292
at dapat handa rin tayo
na labanan siya do'n.

868
00:55:37,917 --> 00:55:41,921
May mga bala at apoy tayo,
pero di nakatulong 'yon sa mga sundalo.

869
00:55:44,507 --> 00:55:45,508
Dapat nando'n ako.

870
00:55:48,094 --> 00:55:49,304
At handa na 'ko.

871
00:55:49,387 --> 00:55:52,724
Handa na 'kong ipakita sa kanya
na di na 'ko natatakot.

872
00:56:09,032 --> 00:56:13,078
Confirmation 'yan.
Nasa patrol si Anderson. Kinumpirma nila.

873
00:56:14,079 --> 00:56:18,333
Solid copy, Bravo One.
Ituloy n'yo ang pagbabantay. Over.

874
00:56:26,299 --> 00:56:27,592
Uy, McConnell.

875
00:56:27,675 --> 00:56:29,969
May delivery ba ngayong gabi
na di ko alam?

876
00:56:30,053 --> 00:56:31,513
Negative, private.

877
00:56:31,596 --> 00:56:33,598
Ano'ng ginagawa mo, pare?

878
00:56:36,726 --> 00:56:38,686
Showtime, Snookums!

879
00:56:39,270 --> 00:56:40,313
Mellon.

880
00:56:45,068 --> 00:56:46,236
Lintik!

881
00:56:48,238 --> 00:56:49,239
Pasensiya na, ha!

882
00:56:50,657 --> 00:56:51,825
Pasok na sa first gate.

883
00:56:51,908 --> 00:56:55,120
Dalawang kalaban, towers,
sa bandang kaliwa.

884
00:57:15,348 --> 00:57:17,142
Eto na tayo sa masaya.

885
00:57:47,046 --> 00:57:49,299
-Halika na! Halika na!
-Tara! Tara!

886
00:57:50,467 --> 00:57:51,843
Sige na! Andar na!

887
00:58:09,652 --> 00:58:10,487
Yown!

888
00:58:12,947 --> 00:58:14,699
Susmaryosep.

889
00:58:15,283 --> 00:58:17,744
Ayos lang ba lahat? Okay lang kayo?

890
00:58:17,827 --> 00:58:19,954
-Oo.
-Ayos ka lang? Ayos lang kayo?

891
00:58:20,914 --> 00:58:22,874
Uy, ang galing mong bumaril, a.

892
00:58:23,541 --> 00:58:24,375
Ikaw rin.

893
00:58:26,711 --> 00:58:29,464
Akala ko ba 'yon ang madaling part?

894
00:58:30,340 --> 00:58:31,382
'Yon nga.

895
00:58:32,050 --> 00:58:33,009
Handa ka na?

896
00:58:35,136 --> 00:58:36,012
Handa na.

897
00:59:51,087 --> 00:59:52,088
Oras na.

